			        DEFAULTCOMMENT="&lt;P&gt;This method makes available the &lt;I&gt;Case&lt;/I&gt; object, named &lt;B&gt;oCase&lt;/B&gt;, which can be used in your calculation to set a &lt;I&gt;System.Boolean&lt;/I&gt; object named &lt;B&gt;AddFee.&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&lt;P&gt;The following example indicates that the Follow-up Inspection Fee is going to be added for Inspection Type of &quot;Safety&quot;:&lt;/P&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&lt;P&gt;AddFee = false&lt;BR&gt;Dim oInsp As Hansen.CDR.CodeEnforcement.IInspection&lt;BR&gt;For Each oInsp In oCase.Inspections&lt;BR&gt;If oInsp.InspectionType.Code.ToUpper() = “SAFETY” Then &lt;BR&gt;AddFee = true&lt;BR&gt;End If&lt;BR&gt;Exit For&lt;BR&gt;Next oInsp&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/P&gt;"/>
