			        DEFAULTCOMMENT="This NextStateFormula Event is for determining the value to be used within a License Application's Next Milestone process.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Available to be used within the formula is a LicenseApplication object expressed as 'oLicenseApp'. The resulting value (the license's next milestone) needs to be set into the variable 'NextState'.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Example:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;'&gt;&lt;span style='color:blue'&gt;If&lt;/span&gt;(oLicenseApp.ProcessState.Code.ToUpper = &lt;span style='color:purple'&gt;&amp;quot;Application Processed&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style='color:blue'&gt;Then&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;NextState&amp;nbsp;=&amp;nbsp;&amp;quot;Application Issued&amp;quot&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style='color:blue'&gt;End&amp;nbsp;If&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;"/>
