			        DEFAULTCOMMENT="&lt;P&gt;This method makes available the &lt;I&gt;BusinessLicense&lt;/I&gt; object, named &lt;STRONG&gt;oLicenseApp&lt;/STRONG&gt;, which can be used in your calculation to set a &lt;I&gt;System.Boolean&lt;/I&gt; object named &lt;B&gt;AddOnCondition&lt;/B&gt;.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;For example, the following formula determines if an address&amp;nbsp;check condition&amp;nbsp;should be added for the license. &lt;/P&gt;&#xA;&#xD;&lt;P&gt;If oLicenseApp.Address.AddressKey&amp;nbsp;&amp;lt;= 1 Then&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;AddOnCondition = True&lt;BR&gt;Else&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;AddOnCondition = False&lt;BR&gt;End If&lt;/P&gt;"/>
