			        DEFAULTCOMMENT="&lt;P&gt;This method makes available the &lt;I&gt;TradeLicenseApplication&lt;/I&gt; object, named &lt;STRONG&gt;oTradeLicense&lt;/STRONG&gt;, which can be used in your calculation to set a &lt;I&gt;System.String&lt;/I&gt; object named &lt;B&gt;PortalDescription&lt;/B&gt;.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;For example, the following formula determines the value of PortalDescription. &lt;/P&gt;dim fees as IFeeCollection =  oTradeLicense.GetProperty(of IFeeCollection)(&quot;Application.Fees&quot;)&lt;/P&gt;  &lt;P&gt;PortalDescription = &quot;Fees Check&quot;&lt;BR&gt;For Each fee As IFee In fees&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;if  fee.TotalUnpaidAmount &gt; 0&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;PortalDescription = &quot;Pay the unpaid balance&quot;&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;end if&lt;BR&gt;Next&lt;/P&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;P&gt;We can also create a HTML value on Agency Variable and use it as value for PortalDescription. For example, we have PortalDescHTML as name in Agency Variable.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/P&gt;dim fees as IFeeCollection =  oTradeLicense.GetProperty(of IFeeCollection)(&quot;Application.Fees&quot;)&lt;/P&gt;  &lt;P&gt;PortalDescription = &quot;Fees Check&quot;&lt;BR&gt;For Each fee As IFee In fees&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;if  fee.TotalUnpaidAmount &gt; 0&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;PortalDescription=ServerApplication.GetAgencyVariableString (&quot;PortalDescHTML&quot;)&lt;BR&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;end if&lt;BR&gt;Next&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;"/>
